---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Our Artisans" description="Learn about the heritage, master blacksmithing craftsmanship, and engineering standards behind The Urban Forge.">
  <Header />
  
  <section class="page-header bg-dark">
    <div class="container relative-z text-center">
      <h1>Artisans of the Anvil & Modern Steel</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">The heritage, craftsmanship, and precision behind The Urban Forge.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="container section">
    <div class="story-section">
      <div class="story-content">
        <h2>Our Heritage</h2>
        <p class="lead">With a 20-year local reputation, we have evolved from traditional welders into true artisans. Our work is not mass-produced; each piece—from grand spiral staircases to intricate fireplace screens—is a unique expression of durability and design.</p>
        <p>At The Urban Forge, we believe that metal is not a cold, rigid medium, but a canvas for texture, form, and legacy. Every hammer blow on our anvils leaves an authentic mark that tells a story of human dedication—a tactile character that a CNC machine simply cannot replicate.</p>
        <p>We partner with high-end architects, structural engineers, and interior designers to seamlessly integrate bespoke metalwork into luxury homes and commercial spaces throughout the region.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="story-image-box">
        <div class="image-overlay-border"></div>
        <img src="/images/architectural_blacksmiths.png" alt="Blacksmith at the anvil" class="about-hero-img" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-bar">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-number">20+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Years of Craftsmanship</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-number">100%</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Bespoke Commissions</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-number">500+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Architectural Installations</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title">Our Guiding Principles</h2>
    <div class="principles-grid">
      <div class="principle-card">
        <div class="card-num">01</div>
        <h3>Traditional Artistry</h3>
        <p>We keep the centuries-old heritage of architectural blacksmithing alive. By combining coal forge techniques with modern metallurgy, we craft one-of-a-kind profiles that stand the test of time.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="principle-card">
        <div class="card-num">02</div>
        <h3>Engineering Rigor</h3>
        <p>Bespoke aesthetics are nothing without safety. We design and construct all handrails, guardrails, and floating staircases to strictly meet or exceed local building codes and load requirements.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="principle-card">
        <div class="card-num">03</div>
        <h3>Uncompromising Finish</h3>
        <p>Our hand-rubbed patinas, statuary bronze processes, and protective matte coatings ensure that every piece retains its deep, rich tonal character for generations, even in coastal environments.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-banner">
      <h3>Let's Forge Your Legacy Piece</h3>
      <p>Whether you have fully realized architectural CAD files or a simple hand sketch, we are ready to collaborate.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn">Start Your Commission</a>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-dark" style="padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0; text-align: center;">
     <p style="color: var(--color-off-white); margin: 0;">&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} The Urban Forge. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: var(--spacing-xxl) 0;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-brushed-brass);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .page-header h1 {
    color: var(--color-brushed-brass);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-off-white);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  .story-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xxl);
  }
  .story-content h2 {
    color: var(--color-matte-black);
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }
  .story-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }
  .story-image-box {
    position: relative;
    padding: 10px;
  }
  .image-overlay-border {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: calc(100% - 20px);
    height: calc(100% - 20px);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-brushed-brass);
    transform: translate(15px, 15px);
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .about-hero-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 4px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }
  .stats-bar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    background: var(--color-matte-black);
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-lg);
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xxl);
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(184, 139, 74, 0.2);
  }
  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }
  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-brushed-brass);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-off-white);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 2.25rem;
  }
  .section-title::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 80px;
    height: 3px;
    background-color: var(--color-brushed-brass);
  }
  .principles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xxl);
  }
  .principle-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-lg);
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .principle-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--color-brushed-brass);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .card-num {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(184, 139, 74, 0.1);
    position: absolute;
    top: 5px;
    right: 15px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .principle-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-matte-black);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .principle-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #666;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .cta-banner {
    background-color: var(--color-charcoal);
    color: var(--color-off-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-xxl);
    border: 1px solid rgba(184, 139, 74, 0.3);
  }
  .cta-banner h3 {
    color: var(--color-brushed-brass);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }
  .cta-banner p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-md) auto;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }
  .cta-banner .btn {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .story-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }
    .story-image-box {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .principles-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .principles-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .stats-bar {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-md);
    }
  }
</style>
